                <Header>Greenhouse Gas Reduction / Sustainable Development</Header>
                <Paragraph>The "Federal Maritime Commission 2017 Strategic Sustainability Performance Plan" is available online. Greenhouse gas reduction is part of the plan.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
            <EntitySourceOfInformation EntitySourceOfInformationId="3009" SortOrder="10">
                <FooterDetails>
                    <Email/>
